headline: Zoetis Appoints Stephanie Tilenius to its Board of Directors
summary: PARSIPPANY, N.J., October 28, 2025--Zoetis Inc. (NYSE: ZTS) today announced the appointment of Stephanie Tilenius to its Board of Directors, effective as of December 1, 2025. Ms. Tilenius brings extensive experience in technology-forward, digital health organizations to the Zoetis Board.
